Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.30,0:22:41.05,Song,,0,0,0,,I'll never forget, looking up at the sky from this hilltop,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.05,0:22:49.52,Song,,0,0,0,,The morning sun so beautiful, on spring days, just us two.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.49,0:22:57.69,Song,,0,0,0,,All the hardships and the sorrows,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.66,0:23:05.87,Song,,0,0,0,,Carry them away gently from this hilltop,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.54,0:23:12.81,Song,,0,0,0,,together with the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.81,0:23:23.22,Song,,0,0,0,,This vast, blue sky—may it never change,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.22,0:23:32.83,Song,,0,0,0,,And may my dearest friends stay just the way they are.
